entry.title: Wild-Haired Former Rocker Promises to Remake Argentina if Elected President
entry.content: Javier Milei says he will permanently sideline establishment politicians from “the political caste” he blames for high inflation.

entry.title: U.N., World Leaders Push to Get Gaza Aid Flowing After Biden Pledge
